<p>To find the bounded area between two <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org=
/wiki/Quadratic_function" title=3D"Quadratic function">quadratic functions<=
/a>, we first subtract one from the other, writing the difference as
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle f(x)-g(x)=3Dax^{2}+bx+c=3Da(x-\alpha )(x-\beta )}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>f</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
        <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
        <mi>g</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mi>a</mi>
        <msup>
          <mi>x</mi>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mn>2</mn>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <mo>+</mo>
        <mi>b</mi>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo>+</mo>
        <mi>c</mi>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mi>a</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
        <mi>=CE=B1<!-- =CE=B1 --></mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
        <mi>=CE=B2<!-- =CE=B2 --></mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle f(x)-g(x)=3Da=
x^{2}+bx+c=3Da(x-\alpha )(x-\beta )}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
